author: @KxNOxUTA
text:
I'm forever amazed about people struggling to do some basic thinking and researching (just scroll down) and keep asking what was going on with Felix. He was injured at the time the video was taken (I'm reading it was supposedly a back injury). 

It's life, they're athletes in many aspects within their business. Sometimes you'll see times where members have health concerns, especially the longer they're working in public. They are working so hard, surely we can be expected to do the very simple work of figuring out the answer to our own very simple question?! Given the natures of such concerns and comment sections, the answers are usually only a few scrolls away. 

I personally appreciate this video for normalising that idols are humans with bad times, not performance machines. They smartly included him into the performance while minding his health and I really appreciate that approachâ£

author: @sinevins
text:
This was interesting, I like Stray Kids in their own way, and really like some of what I have seen in their mv's. But honestly their dance practices rather caught me by surprise. Speaking as someone eith dance experience, I mean not a ton, but some, I am a bit disappointed. They seem to ne hyped up, and their mv's are very striking, but honestly it seems this might be an area the can continue to improve in. Can definitely tell there are different levels of damcing skill, and quite often the energy is up and down. Which can be seen more clearly in some moves that are done eith a bit of lackluster, or a bit sloppy, the energy and execution just isn't there. But later that might not be the case for that same member. Seem like they are doing a lot and maybe that could be an issue, not sure. But it does seem like they could all use more time focusing on just making their basics stronger. Maybe trying some popping exercises might help as well. I want to say, I think a couple lessons with Jhope might so them wonders. Because the choreo seems to definitely have those hitting moments, where if those movements were a bit sharper, it would really pop, so to speak, lol. And when the are synchronized they def. look good, and I loved the ripple turns, it was nice, clean and destinct! Very nice!!!
But I think this is also a bit older of a video, so I am hoping they will continue to work on their synchronization, because cleaning that up can make such a huge difference, especially in a routine ehere there are a lot of things going on, but that they are doing very distinct movements one by one to make up one bigger movement when put altogether. I would say they definitely have potential, hopefully they have kept trying to sharpen their routines, individually but also as a group. Mayne I'll go check out some newer dance videos. Anyways, good video, just keep it up and keep working at it. Try and not forget that you are dancing as a group, one unit. So definitely watch the flow between one another. And always remember your facial expressions. Just a little advice. Keep up the hard work guys!

text: Felix. You have to be one of the biggest blessings on this Earth. I know that I crossed paths with Stray Kids for a reason, and I know you were one of those reasons. Before I even knew anything about Stray Kids, I knew about you. Three years ago, when I got my introduction to K-Pop and was beginning to like quite a few groups, I didnâ€™t know much about Stray Kids, but I did know about you. I couldnâ€™t go anywhere without hearing anybody talk about you, and that was what lead me into wanting to find out more about you, and your position in Stray Kids. I came into the fandom blindly, without knowing any of the names of the members, and relied on the Stay to tell me everything I needed to know about you. It was because of the intense loving fanbase that you have that I learned, in only a matter of days, what a rare talent you are. The depth of your voice combined with your passionate vocals is one of the most beautiful sounds I have ever heard. Your rapping and singing abilities are entirely specific to you and are so captivatingly intriguing, that I knew I loved you from the moment I first got introduced to you. You are so flexible with your voice and on the stage; and once I first got notice of how outstanding you are, I couldnâ€™t stop discovering what made you so enticing and lovable. You are so recognized and appreciated for your natural talent that word reached me about how special you are before I even got a chance to know who Stray Kids really were. Since then, I have been a Stay, and I can say that you are an individual that led me to become one. I have never seen someone with such a bright presence and spirit completely dominant on stage and create an environment so mysterious and energetic for so many people. You bring to music what nobody else can, and I am so happy you share that with all of your Stay when you could be doing something else. I see how happy that you make your members, and since I am a relatively new fan, I still have yet to learn everything that Stray Kids has been through in the years that youâ€™ve been active. However, I have already seen how much you have healed your members when they needed you the most and provided for Stay a support system that they can actually believe in. You are such a delight to be around and I get so happy just seeing your face these days, especially with all of the craziness thatâ€™s in the world. You have a strong-willed heart, and you are extremely kind, forgiving, and non-judgmental. I have loved becoming so acquainted with you and appreciating all of your hard work because you deserve it! You do so much for everyone, and I hope you know that you are so loved and Stay are so grateful to you for even the little things that you do every single day! Never give up and I hope you continue to be the person that uplifts Stay and your members! I know that no matter what happens, Stay will always support you and I canâ€™t tell you how much you really mean to all of us. Thank you so much for being such a kind and loving human being, and for accepting me and so many people into your family as Stay! I pray that you and your loved ones stay safe, and find happiness and worth in the future! On behalf of your friends, members, Stay, and most importantly, your family, I want to wish you the most entertaining and enjoyable birthday ever!! Felix, have fun, PLEASE, PLEASE, PLEASE, stay safe, Happy, Birthday, and WE LOVE YOU!!!!

text: Jisung. Deciding to support Stray Kids has been one of the best decisions of my entire life, and you are one of the people who are the reason why I do so. I only just started supporting K-Pop groups three years ago, and I discovered so many groups because I had the time on my hands. However, since I graduated high school I have found I have been a lot busier and unfortunately havenâ€™t been able to dedicate my time to supporting these groups that I like. I didnâ€™t think that there was going to be any time left for me to support another group, but then you came along. My first experience from Stray Kids was the song â€˜Side Effects,â€™ and it fortunately was a song where I got to hear the vocal and rap blend of your versatile voice. Next, it was â€˜Boxer,â€™ which despite it being an upbeat song, almost moved to to tears because of how beautiful your voice sounded.  After that, I watched you on â€˜The Masked Singer,â€™ and I couldnâ€™t stop from there. I quickly learned that there is nothing that you canâ€™t do. You are a stunning vocalist, flexible rapper, and outstanding dancer. Overall, this allows for you to be one of the most exceptional performers that I, and other Stay, have ever come to know. I knew, right from the moment that I heard your voice, that I had to have more. I kept going, and since then, I have come to learn so much about you and the legacy that you have already left on music. Stay is one of the most unique fandoms that I have been so fortunate to join, and I now know that you are one of the reasons why. I had always thought about Stray Kids as being such an active group and constantly releasing music and content to show how much Stay meant to them, only to find out that you have been such a huge part of that all along. I havenâ€™t even been a Stay for very long yet, but I already have seen the indescribable impact that you left on Stay. It is unlike anything that I have ever seen. I can see how happy, inspired, and desperate that Stay are to reciprocate every ounce of love that you give to them. When I became aware of this, I knew I had to be a part of it. You are so generous, honest, loyal, and possibly most importantly, I have seen you completely change the type of day someone is having just by setting the mood. Whether it be your members, or Stay, you always make sure that everyone is having the best day possible, even it means you have to sacrifice your mood for somebody else. Because you are just naturally funny and inclined to make everybody around you happy, you have an outlook on life that causes everybody you ever meet to be better and happier because of it all. As Iâ€™ve said, I havenâ€™t been a Stay for long at all, but on behalf of the other fans, I already canâ€™t even thank you enough for everything that you do every day. You have such a refreshing personality that we all need, especially at this time in the world. text: Seungmin, I would like to wish you an early happy birthday, as the time is drawing close. My introduction to Stray Kids was unique in that the reason I decided to support it was because of the fans. I have been a K-Pop fan for almost a decade, and I have come to support many groups. However, becoming a Stay was a new experience for me because it was the first time that I joined a group because the love from the fans was so strong, I knew I needed to be a part of it. I learned about each Stray Kids member one at a time, and what I learned and admired very quickly about you was your individuality. Every member stands out for their own reasons, but your charm is retaining your individuality and independence while still being a part of something bigger. I became an official Stay two years ago, and since then I have gotten to see how well you blend in with your members. You are such a valued member of Stray Kids, that we canâ€™t see them existing without you. Youâ€™ve also created a journey of personal growth and development both musically and personally and I have felt so connected to you since Iâ€™ve become a Stay. Your personality is so enticing in that sometimes you can be quiet and shy, but other times you are very vocal and humorous with your members. Itâ€™s very powerful that you can be so sweet and naturally kind-hearted without saying any words sometimes, while other times, being open and direct about how you feel. I can see how much your loving personality has impacted your members, because Iâ€™ve never seen them happier than when you spend time with them. You are always making your members laugh and motivating them just by putting one smile on their face. I feel so inspired watching you build such a trustworthy relationship with them and want to be at least half as generous as you. I know that your members are so thankful for you everyday and couldnâ€™t be anywhere near as successful without you. I have never heard a fanbase talk so highly and frequently of a member in the way that they honor you. I always hear Stay talking about how gentle and sweet you are; and how much positivity and love you bring to the world wherever you go. Stay talk about your rare, emotion-based, and versatile voice that captivates everyone into your performance. They talk about the flawless and effortless dancing that you work so hard to share with us and spoil us with on every stage. They talk about your overall professional and inspirational performance on stage that leaves every Stay wanting to spend more time with you. Iâ€™ve heard so much about how beloved you are Seungmin, and once I became a Stay, I am seeing for myself how much you are adored all over the world. Not only by Stay, but the loving influence that you have on your members makes them and everyone that you meet a kinder and more loving person. Stay praise and speak so highly of you, that I canâ€™t say Iâ€™ve experienced a family this loving toward an idol. I just want you know how much love there is everywhere all around the world for you. You are the reason that so many people lift their heads up and keep going another day, including me. There is so much negativity going on in the world right now, and to have you as a role model and see it not preventing you from sharing more love is making the world even stronger and closer to restoring to its greatness. I really feel like we donâ€™t deserve you sometimes because your genuine strong heart is hard to come across these days. I hope that we can repay you even a little bit of the love youâ€™ve shown us in just a few years since your debut. I know you have worked so hard to be where you are and I donâ€™t even want to pretend to know how much youâ€™ve probably gone through. I just want to take this day, and every day afterwards to recognize and let you become aware of how much I, Stay, and your members really love you. I know that your parents and the rest of your family are prouder of you than any other person and they respond to every action you take with great respect, understanding, and love. Your members and family are so lucky to have you and I know that are thankful and appreciative of you every day. Thank you so much for sacrificing more than we know just to make us happy even a little bit. On behalf of your friends, members, Stay, and loving family, I hope that the love that you have given to this world is given back to you on this special day and every day in your future. Please surround yourself by the people that love you most, and let the love that we have for you give you the most fulfillment! I wish you nothing but happiness for you and your loved ones, and I pray that you all stay safe!! Happy birthday Seungmin!! We adore you so much and we are so grateful to have such a bright light in our lives!!!

text: Changbin. Iâ€™m so fortunate to be able to celebrate your birthday with the rest of Stays. I would like to talk about your musicality. Iâ€™ve never heard anybody rap like you, and I know I wonâ€™t hear anybody rap like you for the rest of my life. You have this growl, this grit, that is enough to supply every word you say with the perfect amount of power and character that it needs. No matter what the circumstance is for your song, you retain this originality and this sound that nobody else has. The connection between the raps you create and your execution of them is simply seamless.  Your lyrical style is mesmerizing, and watching these musical ideas pop into your head like second nature is truly astonishing. You can also sing beautifully as well, and the rough texture of your voice gives you this edge that lights up all of your lines. It is rare to see somebody be able to master both singing and rapping, and the unique sound of your voice allows for you to become limitless through both. You are also an incredibly skilled dancer. Your moves are so natural, and watching you feels surreal because you become so immersed in your movement. You absorb all of these choreographies, and then interpret them in such a realistic and emotional way. You have so much power and when you dance, yet you have the right amount of control to give off just the perfect amount of expression. You give care to each little gesture, and treat each move with such delicacy. It is a journey from start to finish when you dance, and you take all of us with you without missing a single detail along the way. Overall, you are one among other artists that sincerely represent our generation and capture its essence. Your innovation and relationship with music are so complex and clear at the same time. You are young, but as you become older and more experienced, there is no telling what youâ€™re already curious and inventive mind will supply to the world. Your impact on music and your Stay will be timeless. At the same time that I love your musicality, I love your personality as well. I first noticed that you are so laid-back and have this calming demeanor. You are also unexpectedly hilarious. You make jokes in moments where nobody anticipates and you can change the entire mood of a situation in mere seconds. You are so humble, and place those around you before you no matter what the circumstances. Though I have never met you in person, you have to be one of the best people to be around and I know that your members know this better than anybody else. You really hold your team down, and together, and always find a way to make sure everybody feels included. It has only been a short time since Iâ€™ve known you, but I saw almost instantly how your members individually love and cherish you in their own special way. You bring the excitement and thrill of life to them wherever and whenever they need it. You have the biggest heart. You have stood your members up time and time again and pointed them in the right direction if ever they forget what they are chasing after. You are somebody they can lean on through all instances in their life; and have become their brother. We all know that you provide your members with a love that they could not get from anybody else. Though they are all different, you find a way to embrace this and form a sacred relationship with each of them. I know that they will continue to grow and develop, but only with you by their side to guide them through it all. They will continue to be the best versions of themselves and there is nothing that can hold them back because you believe in them with all of your heart and soul. Your love will always trail them and aid them for the rest of their lives. Thank you for raising them, and changing their lives forever so that they can lead the fullest life possible. I want to personally thank your family and parents for raising you and helping you become the aspiring young man you are today. I know how much your family means to you, and you have firsthand showed us what they mean to you and how you spend your time with them. It is clear to see that you already keep this in mind with you at all times, but I just want to say that I hope you can always rely on them in your life when you find you need somebody. When you find yourself having troubles down the line, I hope you can remember the feeling of being with them to restore you to your former state of peace and optimism. Your family loves you more than anybody else on this planet, and I hope you know that when you feel there is nobody who can understand, they will always be there to help you out of any tough situation. They are the most proud of you, will always be the most proud of you, and you honor them with every step you take towards your dream. As Stay, we keep them in our hearts as you do and hope to become as dedicated and authentic through all that we do as they are. Changbin, it is often said that Stay are the luckiest fandom in the world, and I can wholeheartedly agree with that as you are responsible for the truth behind this. You are extremely sensitive and considerate of all of our feelings, and that is perhaps one of the aspects of you that I love the most. You seem to always listen to what we have to say and are even eager to respond to it. When discussing Stay with your members or others, you always have the most original ideas and show us how much you love us through your own eyes. When we chose to become a Stay, you chose us. Your world opened up to us and you invited us to become every bit of a part of you as your members and family.  Similarly to your members, there are Stay from all over the world who come from different backgrounds, and it is only because of you that we are able to come together in unity. I know itâ€™s not always easy to let us in and to see us while youâ€™re in a tough situation, but the fact that you put your fears aside and show up for us every time is the greatest testament of your love for us. You are the first person we turn to when we are down and need cheering up. It is truly the greatest honor getting to be the ones that you work so hard for and trust it all to. You have faith in us when we donâ€™t, and it gives us enough confidence to tackle whatever is thrown at us. Thank you for loving us unconditionally, and being there when nobody else has. Thank you for changing our lives, and being at the heart of the greatest days of our lives. I know that youâ€™ve been through a lot, and youâ€™ve only been active with Stray kids for a few mere years. Iâ€™ve seen firsthand how it took all you had and then some to even debut, and there have been too many struggles since then that youâ€™ve faced. The best that I can do, knowing that youâ€™ve been in these difficult situations more than anybody should be in, is try to imagine how it feels to be in your shoes. I know that itâ€™s been a lot. All that I can say, on behalf of all of your loved ones, that we are so proud of you for making it past all of these moments. You have a heart a gold and always keep your head up even when it feels impossible, and I know that this is the reason why youâ€™ve been able to persevere through all that youâ€™ve been through. We know that you can take charge and make it out of whatever happens in the future. I hope that this birthday makes all of your dreams come true and that you accmplish all that you desire on this special day. I often wonder of when you get to take a break and truly look back on the impact that youâ€™ve had on the world, so I hope that if anything, your special day provides you for the perfect opportunity to do that. I hope you are able to look at the countless hearts that you touch every day around the world in limitless ways, and let that make you feel as loved and honored as youâ€™ve ever felt. I hope that those around you also help you to see how worthy of love and commemoration that you truly are. Please relax today and I hope that you spend every second making precious memories. I hope that this day goes down as one of the greatest youâ€™ve had in a while. You deserve all of the sucess and blessings, and I know that more will only come to you. Thank you for sacrificing so much just to make Stray Kids and several other projects possible. Thank you for suffering through any pain, concern, fear, doubt, isolation, confusion, fatigue, stress, and so much more just to bring us any content at all. I hope that you never feel pressured or obligated to change because you are a rare gem of a human being. The world, and more specifically, your Stay need you just as you are to continue to inspire us and remind us what it is to love others and yourself in daily life. You are beautiful inside and out, and perfect as you are. I hope you remember we always will support you no matter what! author: @RM_formerlyjustRMbutYTsucks
text:
-I.N slowly adopting the crop top agenda.

- I love how well they blend. They're all, at minimum, good dancers, but the group as a whole always looks so great when they dance because the ones with a higher level tend to work to match with the others, which keeps members from standing out when they shouldn't and makes the entire group look better than if you have one person showing off. _Not_ standing out/drawing attention when you shouldn't is an actual skill, one that's very undervalued by the general public.

- Go _off,_ I.N! Boy went all in on this! His vocals and dance have both shown so much growth this last year.

- That is the best view we've gotten so far of the volcano ripple. It looks so GOOD here! I wish the camera work on the stages was showing it better.

- The second drill chorus is a ripple! It's so closely timed, and there's usually so much else going on, that I hadn't caught that before. But it's a ripple on sixteenth notes. SIXTEENTH notes. They divided one beat into a perfect four-part ripple. Wtf.

- ğŸ˜¥watching Felix over in the doorway dancing along with his hands.

- Seo Changbin, sir. We see you doing the "popping" thrusts in the same choreographed form as everyone else. Which means your evolution into dropping your arm back behind your a$$ so you can _really_ pop that pelvis in performances is 100% deliberate. There's a Lee Know soundclip out there full of utter BS about "It's part of the choreo" that I am now also applying to you.

I wish company and choreographer gives them less tiring/fatiguing and hard choreographies in the future, my heart breaks when they got injured, their health should be priority!! There're so many options how make easy but still eye catching chore. Our 8 boys are our priority and their health!!! 
Thanks for always working so hard, we see everything, WE LOVE YOU â£ï¸
It's biggest flex to stan such a group like SKZ, being loved as fan and being mind blown each comeback how they outdo themselves.

author: @kellykuk
text:
I absolutely adore watching the dance practices! We get to see the raw dance routine before any necessary tweeks are made. We get to see the Kids in 'working mode' and you can ALMOST hear them thinking, "I've gotta put the foot there! I've gotta land here!" 

The MANIAC dance routine has become a personal favourite of mine. I just love how disconnected and disjointed it is, just like the song so it goes incredibly well.

One thing that I also like is the fact that it's clearly been designed with Felixs back injury in mind but in such a way that he can still participate, however limited it may be. It also looks easy to adapt if and when Felix has been given the 'all clear' by his doctor and/or his physiotherapist. 

Thank you for giving us STAY this generous gift. We appreciate it so much. Keep up this amazing work. We love you so much. 

Kindest regards,
Kady xx
